    <section>
        <title>Basic formatting</title>
        <para>Paragraphs are wrapped in "para" and "/para" tags. To add particual font effects to indidual words and sentences, you can apply tags before and after the items you wish to modify.</para>
        <para>italics:<emphasis>This is a paragraph.</emphasis></para>
        <para>bold: <emphasis role="bold">This is a paragraph.</emphasis></para>
        <para>underline: <emphasis role="underline">This is a paragraph.</emphasis></para>
        <para>superscript. The next line includes a superscript and subscript.</para> 
        <para>The calculation is X<subscript>a</subscript><superscript>2</superscript> + X<subscript>a</subscript><superscript>3</superscript>.</para>
        
    </section> 
       
